    dcterms:modified "2024-03-28T17:03:59+00:00" ;
    schema1:description "Carol has a rich and diverse career leading some of the most transformative public-sector change programmes of the last two decades. As Executive Director for Government People Group, Carol leads a cross-government programme on Line Management Capability for the Civil Service as well as being a Non Executive Director for the Government Property Agency. Previously, as Director of People & Places and Executive Committee member for the Cabinet Office, she spearheaded a significant reorganisation to achieve an unprecedented change to the geographical footprint."@en ;
    schema1:name "Carol Bernard CBE"@en ;
